Description: PeaZip free file archiver utility, GTK2 build
 PeaZip is an Open Source (LGPLv3) cross-platform archive manager utility, 
 supporting over 200 archiving and compression formats as 7Z, BZip2, Brotli, 
 GZip, PEA, RAR, ZIP, ZPAQ, Zstandard, and many more.

